Strata Worldwide returns to Sydney Olympic Park next month to showcase its line of engineered roof support products, its selection of emergency refuge shelters, the completely wireless and battery-powered StrataConnect™ Wireless system and of course, HazardAvert®, the global-leading solution in proximity detection and collision avoidance. Strata will also unveiling upgrades to its wireless communication system – upgrades that will significantly improve usability and increase functionality for miners underground. In addition, through a successful partnership with RFI Technology Solutions of Sydney, Strata has something new in its portfolio: a technology that will expand on how mines use their leaky feeder systems. Visit us in stand B121 to find out more and speak to Strata professionals at AIMEX between 27 and 29 August in Sydney.